___________________________________________________________
!! IMPORTANT !!
 Dependencies:
 1 OS: ubuntu 12.04
 2 ROS: groovy
 3 ros-groovy-openni-*
 4 NITE-Bin-Dev-Linux-x86-v1.5.2.21 (strictly)
 5 gnuplot

 USAGE prerequisites:
 1 roscore running
 2 rosrun openni_tracker openni_tracker running
 3 rosrun rviz rviz (for debug use)
 
 Procedure:
 1 Have met the Prerequisites
 2 Run the collectTrainingSetData.sh
 3 Run the collectTestSetData.sh
 4 Run the trainSVM.sh to get the svm model in svm/tools dir
 5 Run the offlineTest.sh  or onlineTest.sh
